It'll lead to
a destructive fight with you.

00:23:09.040 --> 00:23:11.810
She sent you as a sacrificial pawn

00:23:12.480 --> 00:23:14.020
because she's too afraid

00:23:14.040 --> 00:23:16.020
to charge in and go down with me.

00:23:16.830 --> 00:23:19.740
You can keep talking without worry.

00:23:46.550 --> 00:23:47.530
