00:24:36.150 --> 00:24:37.260
let alone poisoned anyone.

00:24:37.680 --> 00:24:39.700
But with just that scar on the palm

00:24:40.520 --> 00:24:41.530
and your secret telegram,

00:24:41.550 --> 00:24:44.260
it's enough for her to accuse you

00:24:44.720 --> 00:24:45.700
before the Japanese military leadership.

00:24:47.760 --> 00:24:49.740
As long as Taro is still alive,

00:24:50.200 --> 00:24:52.810
her lie falls apart instantly.

00:24:54.040 --> 00:24:55.420
How could the Tonoji family

00:24:55.680 --> 00:24:57.460
be so foolish?

00:24:59.630 --> 00:25:00.570
Major General,

00:25:02.040 --> 00:25:05.220
you can't believe that Taro was killed

00:25:05.240 --> 00:25:08.700
by an anti-Japanese operative, right?

00:25:13.720 --> 00:25:15.740
Lin Megumi.

00:25:16.720 --> 00:25:17.420
Major General,

00:25:18.680 --> 00:25:20.180
right now the Tonoji family members

00:25:20.200 --> 00:25:21.220
are lying in wait outside.

00:25:21.550 --> 00:25:22.740
With your skills,

00:25:22.760 --> 00:25:24.260
you could launch a surprise attack

00:25:24.280 --> 00:25:26.220
and wipe them out completely.

00:25:26.680 --> 00:25:28.740
