00:25:29.590 --> 00:25:30.770
everyone here tonight

00:25:30.790 --> 00:25:32.220
can testify for you

00:25:32.240 --> 00:25:33.770
that it was them who struck first,

00:25:33.790 --> 00:25:36.220
and you were only defending yourself.

00:25:53.550 --> 00:25:55.740
Miss Megumi, please show up.

00:25:56.520 --> 00:25:58.980
Miss Megumi, please show up.

00:25:59.790 --> 00:26:02.660
Miss Megumi, please show up.

00:26:02.760 --> 00:26:03.810
Miss Megumi.

00:26:04.830 --> 00:26:05.900
Miss Megumi.

00:26:07.200 --> 00:26:08.260
Miss Megumi.

00:26:15.150 --> 00:26:16.260
Should we go in now?

00:26:17.040 --> 00:26:17.980
Hold on.

00:26:19.150 --> 00:26:20.020
It's a trap.

00:26:52.480 --> 00:26:54.180
A message just came from the hospital.

00:26:54.200 --> 00:26:56.290
Xian Biyun helped us find our radio

00:26:56.310 --> 00:26:57.290
and the operator.

00:26:57.310 --> 00:26:59.770
But the operator already confessed.

00:27:00.310 --> 00:27:02.460
Lin Megumi got our transmission records.

00:27:02.480 --> 00:27:04.260
It's likely reported to the leadership.

00:27:06.240 --> 00:27:07.980
Tell him to deal with the traitor.

00:27:08.480 --> 00:27:12.500
Then bring Xian Biyun here.

00:27:13.310 --> 00:27:14.770
I have questions for her.

00:27:15.040 --> 00:27:16.020
Understood.

00:27:17.200 --> 00:27:18.180
Understood.

00:27:19.960 --> 00:27:20.940
What do you think, Major General?

00:27:22.070 --> 00:27:23.180
I wasn't lying, was I?

00:27:24.480 --> 00:27:26.290
I'll wait for her to show up.

00:27:26.310 --> 00:27:28.020
Let her explain herself.

00:27:28.960 --> 00:27:30.770
You want to confront Lin Megumi?

00:27:31.550 --> 00:27:32.980
But she seems to be hiding something.

00:27:33.000 --> 00:27:34.660
She thinks it's just a trap in there.

00:27:35.070 --> 00:27:36.260
She's not coming in at all.

00:27:43.240 --> 00:27:44.740
What if I have a way

00:27:46.760 --> 00:27:48.740
to get her inside?

00:27:54.760 --> 00:27:55.900
How's that?

00:28:13.280 --> 00:28:14.020
Hurry!

00:28:14.040 --> 00:28:15.020
Hurry!

00:28:15.040 --> 00:28:16.180
Hurry!

00:28:16.760 --> 00:28:18.020
It's time.

00:28:19.480 --> 00:28:21.220
Go in with me!

00:28:21.240 --> 00:28:21.980
Yes.

00:28:37.920 --> 00:28:39.420
It's a trap. Get out.

00:28:39.440 --> 00:28:40.180
Yes.

00:29:07.520 --> 00:29:08.220
Lin Megumi.

00:29:09.280 --> 00:29:11.500
