00:29:13.280 --> 00:29:14.420
You framed me for plotting
against the Duke.

00:29:14.440 --> 00:29:16.420
I've informed General Yasui.

00:29:17.110 --> 00:29:18.740
He's on his way now.

00:29:19.070 --> 00:29:22.660
As long as you face the trial calmly

00:29:23.150 --> 00:29:25.090
and tell everything truthfully,

00:29:25.630 --> 00:29:27.330
the Tonoji family can still survive.

00:29:28.310 --> 00:29:31.740
Otherwise, stirring up infighting

00:29:32.480 --> 00:29:37.220
is enough to get your family wiped out.

00:29:39.390 --> 00:29:41.130
You need to think this through.

00:29:51.790 --> 00:29:54.900
Your son poisoned Dr. Edward.

00:29:55.550 --> 00:29:58.940
I saw it with my own eyes.

00:30:00.240 --> 00:30:02.090
Is that what you call framing too?

00:30:07.760 --> 00:30:09.050
And that con man?

00:30:09.520 --> 00:30:11.180
You mean Joseph Lee?

00:30:13.200 --> 00:30:14.940
He's an imposter.

00:30:14.960 --> 00:30:16.740
His real name is Ding Yi.

00:30:16.760 --> 00:30:19.260
He's a true anti-Japanese operative.

00:30:20.040 --> 00:30:21.530
He murdered Joseph Lee,

00:30:21.550 --> 00:30:23.260
then took over his identity.

00:30:24.040 --> 00:30:24.700
Major General.

00:30:29.760 --> 00:30:32.090
Isn't that exactly what I just said?

00:30:32.480 --> 00:30:34.850
She'll accuse me
of being an anti-Japanese operative.

00:30:34.870 --> 00:30:38.420
She might even claim I'm not Joseph Lee.

00:30:38.440 --> 00:30:39.740
If I guessed right,

00:30:39.760 --> 00:30:40.740
next...

00:30:40.760 --> 00:30:42.420
she'll say right away,

00:30:42.440 --> 00:30:43.090
I'm just

00:30:43.110 --> 00:30:45.370
an actress in my wife's troupe.

00:30:45.390 --> 00:30:46.460
She might even insult me,

00:30:46.480 --> 00:30:48.460
claiming I'm not really blind.

00:30:49.960 --> 00:30:50.610
Major General,

00:30:51.440 --> 00:30:52.460
she's completely lost it.

00:30:52.960 --> 00:30:53.850
This woman

00:30:53.960 --> 00:30:56.660
is desperate
to inherit the Tonoji family.

00:30:57.310 --> 00:30:59.090
She'll say anything to get it.

00:31:00.390 --> 00:31:01.500
But Miss Megumi,

00:31:01.870 --> 00:31:02.740
you should know,

00:31:02.760 --> 00:31:04.260
I've worked with the Major General

00:31:04.280 --> 00:31:06.700
for a full year.

00:31:07.520 --> 00:31:09.090
If I weren't Joseph Lee,

00:31:09.390 --> 00:31:11.740
how would I know how to design a cipher?

00:31:11.760 --> 00:31:13.130
How could I help the Major General solve

00:31:13.150 --> 00:31:14.940
one tricky problem after another?

00:31:15.520 --> 00:31:16.900
Are Dr. Miyamoto,

00:31:16.920 --> 00:31:19.850
Lieutenant Colonel Takeda,
Liang Jingyuan,

00:31:19.870 --> 00:31:24.130
and even Major General all fools?

00:31:28.720 --> 00:31:29.610
Yes, they are.

00:31:29.760 --> 00:31:31.130
Of course, they are.

00:31:31.150 --> 00:31:33.850
The cipher intelligence system
of the China Expeditionary Army in Shanghai,

00:31:33.870 --> 00:31:35.090
from top to bottom,

00:31:35.110 --> 00:31:39.130
has been spun around
by a small-time actor.

00:31:39.150 --> 00:31:40.940
If that's not foolish, what is?

00:31:43.440 --> 00:31:44.500
Lin Megumi,

00:31:46.000 --> 00:31:47.220
